<br />\n獅子山下的香港抗爭者，聲音嚮徹九龍半島處處燈光。這邊廂的機場抗爭者，雖心繫機場卻無處著力。有見及此，以上成員代表聯盟成立新機場公海，準備在我們的家、我們的陣地裡，向世界展示香港人的驕傲，與及堅定對抗人治的決心。<br />\n<br />\n若你同意香港國際機場需要<strong>以和理非、以至和理優</strong>的方式持續影響這場運動，持續表達香港人的聲音，請以行動說明一切，與我們一起成為真機場公海，擁護香港人智取天下的價值、無遠弗屆的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n投票區：@hkairportpoll<br />\n公海link : <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NPwO8BV4k5vTRIsZKJFIOA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNPwO8BV4k5vTRIsZKJFIOA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=c39fa3d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NPwO8BV4k5vTRIsZKJFIOA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6bmTFj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6bmTFj.png&h=824b8b4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"集會都支持 凡搞機場都推"},{"pid":"435504f654b5c940f5fa1520dadd21c3bcbb0d54","tid":1504493,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"機場係戰線"},{"pid":"c64091733caa9e5884328250ad5c34c3ead2b91d","tid":1504493,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ef202995f7435f833d04d3eb901107aa449c95","tid":1504493,"uid":202724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"828國泰城見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd2dedf83180df7baa3eefc0aff94a8af197222","tid":1504493,"uid":202724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:39:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1367c049de9eadba2c2840c9b61ac9523c22fef","tid":1504493,"uid":202724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24e253a3c0ca37dfbb451d5b283d29c5038a395f","tid":1504493,"uid":110509